    <description
  >This template is used to calculate the score and the summary after the response session is submitted</description>
    <developerName>Calculate_User_Score_and_Summary</developerName>
    <masterLabel>Calculate User Score and Summary</masterLabel>
    <templateVersions>
        <content>Calculate the Score and Summary based on the input as follows:

Calculate Score:
From the {!$RelatedList:Response_Session_Id.User_Responses__r.Records}, Query the records to get the MM_Calculated_Score__c field value for all the records.
Sum all the MM_Calculated_Score__c field values for all the records to calculate the score

Calculate Summary:
You&apos;re a mental health expert. Based on the score calculated above , provide a summary of the mental health condition of the user.

Output Format:
The output should be in below format:
{
&quot;Score&quot;: 20,
&quot;Summary&quot;: &quot;You&apos;re suffering from depression&quot;
}


</content>
        <generationTemplateConfigs>
            <generationConfigDeveloperName
      >einstein_gpt__enUsLanguageStyle</generationConfigDeveloperName>
        </generationTemplateConfigs>
        <inputs>
            <apiName>Response_Session_Id</apiName>
            <definition>SOBJECT://MM_Response_Session__c</definition>
            <masterLabel>Response Session Id</masterLabel>
            <referenceName>Input:Response_Session_Id</referenceName>
            <required>true</required>
        </inputs>
        <primaryModel
    >sfdc_ai__DefaultBedrockAnthropicClaude45Haiku</primaryModel>
        <status>Published</status>
        <templateDataProviders>
            <definition>invocable://getRelatedList</definition>
            <parameters>
                <definition>primitive://String</definition>
                <isRequired>true</isRequired>
                <parameterName>parentRecordId</parameterName>
                <valueExpression
        >{!$Input:Response_Session_Id.Id}</valueExpression>
            </parameters>
            <parameters>
                <definition>primitive://String</definition>
                <isRequired>true</isRequired>
                <parameterName>relatedListName</parameterName>
                <valueExpression>User_Responses__r</valueExpression>
            </parameters>
            <referenceName
      >RelatedList:Response_Session_Id.User_Responses__r.Records</referenceName>
        </templateDataProviders>
